WEBVTT

01:48.583 --> 01:50.792
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:50.792 --> 01:53.542
Dexter: WHAT IF THE ICE-TRUCK
KILLER DOES DISAPPEAR?

01:53.542 --> 01:56.542
NO, HE'S GOT
UNFINISHED BUSINESS WITH ME.

01:56.542 --> 01:59.208
"DEAR KEN, I'M IN PIECES.

01:59.208 --> 02:02.083
WHY THE COLD SHOULDER?
LOVE, BARBIE."

02:02.083 --> 02:03.792
Rita:
PAUL CALLED AFTER YOU LEFT.

02:03.792 --> 02:05.667
HE'S ALREADY OUT OF JAIL --
OVERCROWDING.

02:05.667 --> 02:06.875
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?

02:06.875 --> 02:08.458
ARE YOU FUCKING MY WIFE?

02:09.333 --> 02:12.834
Rita: NEXT TIME, WE'LL FIGURE
OUT WHAT TO TELL THE KIDS

02:12.834 --> 02:14.625
SO YOU DON'T HAVE
TO SNEAK OUT LIKE THIS.

02:14.625 --> 02:17.542
YOU WANT THERE
TO BE A NEXT TIME?

02:17.542 --> 02:19.250
I JUST WISH YOU'D GO AWAY.

02:19.250 --> 02:21.500
WHY CAN'T YOU JUST GO AWAY
AND DISAPPEAR FOREVER?

02:21.500 --> 02:23.166
I SO WANT TO MAUL YOU
RIGHT NOW.

02:23.166 --> 02:24.750
I SO WANT YOU TO.

02:24.750 --> 02:27.041
IT'S DIFFERENT.

02:27.041 --> 02:31.083
IT FEELS LIKE...

02:31.083 --> 02:34.917
I HATE SAYING THIS.
IT SOUNDS FUCKING CHEESY.

02:34.917 --> 02:37.083
IT FEELS LIKE MAKING LOVE.

02:38.834 --> 02:41.750
Rudy:
"BARBIE, BE PATIENT.

02:41.750 --> 02:44.250
ONE DAY
WE'LL SHARE A COLD ONE."

03:07.291 --> 03:09.125
Dexter:
THANK GOD FOR SHOWERS.

03:09.125 --> 03:11.083
PRIVATE TIME TO THINK --

03:11.083 --> 03:14.750
HARDER TO COME BY NOW THAT
I'M IN A REAL RELATIONSHIP.

03:14.750 --> 03:16.166
[ DOOR OPENS ]

03:16.166 --> 03:17.709
DO YOU MIND?

03:17.709 --> 03:19.750
NOT AT ALL.

03:19.750 --> 03:22.458
COULD YOU PASS THE SOAP?

03:22.458 --> 03:23.709
YEAH.

03:28.542 --> 03:29.542
OOH!

03:29.542 --> 03:30.834
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

03:30.834 --> 03:32.709
Cody: IT'S LOCKED!

03:32.709 --> 03:35.667
MOM, I GOT TO PEE!

03:35.667 --> 03:37.792
UH, I'LL BE RIGHT THERE,
SWEETIE!

03:37.792 --> 03:40.000
HOLD ON A SECOND,
BUDDY!
I CAN'T!

03:40.000 --> 03:42.792
SWEETIE.
ONE-BATHROOM HOUSE.

03:42.792 --> 03:44.834
NATURE CALLS.

03:47.250 --> 03:50.166
COOL. HOW DID YOU GET
THAT UGLY SCAR?

03:50.166 --> 03:51.667
[ Chuckling ] CODY.

03:51.667 --> 03:52.917
SWORD FIGHT -- I WON.

03:55.166 --> 03:57.458
MOM, I GOT TO BRUSH.

03:57.458 --> 03:59.000
WHATEVER HAPPENED
TO KNOCKING?

03:59.000 --> 04:00.417
I'M GONNA BE
LATE FOR SCHOOL.

04:00.417 --> 04:02.667
YOU BRUSH, YOU PEE,
I'M JUST GONNA...

04:02.667 --> 04:04.834
[ SIGHS ]

04:04.834 --> 04:06.583
WOW, BIG SCAR.

04:06.583 --> 04:10.208
SWORD FIGHT -- HE WON.

04:14.792 --> 04:17.041
Angel: I MEAN, WHAT DOES
"SEPARATION" MEAN TO YOU?

04:17.041 --> 04:19.875
WHAT "SEPARATION" MEANS TO ME
IS THAT YOU'RE SEPARATED,

04:19.875 --> 04:21.166
AND YOU WORK IT OUT.

04:21.166 --> 04:23.041
NOW, THIS WAS
FALSE PRETENSES.

04:23.041 --> 04:25.166
I MEAN, I KNEW
SHE WANTED A DIVORCE

04:25.166 --> 04:27.375
WHEN SHE ASKED FOR
THE SEPARATION -- SHE LIED.

04:27.375 --> 04:28.875
YEAH, AND YOU DIDN'T WHEN YOU
WERE CHEATING ON HER, RIGHT?

04:28.875 --> 04:30.834
"CHEAT" -- ONE CHEAT.

04:30.834 --> 04:31.959
THAT'S IN THE SINGULAR.

04:31.959 --> 04:33.250
ONE. OKAY.

04:33.250 --> 04:35.250
AND I FELT SO CRAPPY,
I TOLD HER THE NEXT DAY.

04:35.250 --> 04:37.041
THAT'S YOUR PROBLEM.
YOU'RE TOO DAMN HONEST.

04:37.041 --> 04:38.917
SHE WOULDN'T EVEN
TALK ABOUT IT.

04:38.917 --> 04:41.125
AND I TRIED TO GET HER TO SEE
A COUNSELOR WITH ME.

04:41.125 --> 04:43.542
STOP THE CAR, MAN!
STOP THE GODDAMN CAR!

04:43.542 --> 04:46.083
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

04:46.083 --> 04:47.375
HEY!

05:02.250 --> 05:04.417
STOP! POLICE!

05:18.917 --> 05:21.667
[ GUNSHOTS ]

05:21.667 --> 05:22.917
DOAKES!

05:22.917 --> 05:25.417
DOAKES!

05:32.917 --> 05:34.792
YOU ALL RIGHT?

05:34.792 --> 05:36.542
YEAH.

06:02.917 --> 06:05.375
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

06:09.834 --> 06:12.208
THE SUSPECT'S NAME
WAS JACQUES BAYARD,

06:12.208 --> 06:14.125
ACCORDING
TO HIS DRIVER'S LICENSE.

06:14.125 --> 06:15.250
HAITIAN?

06:15.250 --> 06:17.041
THAT'D BE MY GUESS.

06:17.041 --> 06:19.291
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S GO OVER IT AGAIN.

06:19.291 --> 06:21.208
I SAW A GUN
IN THE SUSPECT'S WAISTBAND.

06:21.208 --> 06:23.625
I WENT TO QUESTION HIM,
AND HE TOOK OFF RUNNING.

06:23.625 --> 06:26.125
ANGEL, YOU SAW ALL THIS.

06:26.125 --> 06:28.166
YEAH, I SAW BAYARD BOLT,

06:28.166 --> 06:30.166
AND I TURNED THE CAR
AROUND IN PURSUIT.

06:30.166 --> 06:32.333
ALL RIGHT, AND WHEN YOU WENT
UNDER THE CAUSEWAY...

06:32.333 --> 06:34.041
HE TOOK A SHOT AT ME.

06:34.041 --> 06:37.834
I TOOK COVER AND RETURNED FIRE
FROM THAT CORNER.

06:37.834 --> 06:40.208
NO, NOT FROM THERE.

06:40.208 --> 06:42.333
YEAH,
FROM FUCKING RIGHT THERE.

06:42.333 --> 06:45.291
BUT...
[ SIGHS ]

06:45.291 --> 06:48.000
IF YOU SHOT HIM
FROM RIGHT THERE,

06:48.000 --> 06:50.041
THE BLOOD SPATTER WOULD GO
IN THAT DIRECTION.

06:50.041 --> 06:52.166
YOU QUESTIONING ME?
'CAUSE I GOT QUESTIONS FOR YOU.

06:52.166 --> 06:54.500
THE MAN'S JUST DOING
WHAT HE'S SUPPOSED TO DO.

06:54.500 --> 06:56.250
THE MAN IS
A FUCKING CREEP JOB!

06:56.250 --> 06:58.375
JUST FOCUS
ON THE FACTS, OKAY?

06:58.375 --> 07:00.458
THE D.A.'s TEAM
IS READY FOR YOU. YOU GOOD?

07:00.458 --> 07:01.834
I'M GOOD.

07:01.834 --> 07:03.583
YEAH.

07:03.583 --> 07:04.792
YOU'RE UP NEXT.

07:10.542 --> 07:12.917
SORRY, BUT I DIDN'T
INVENT PHYSICS.

07:12.917 --> 07:14.792
HE JUST GOT
MIXED UP IS ALL.

07:14.792 --> 07:17.542
HELL, I'M NOT EVEN SURE
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED.

07:17.542 --> 07:20.041
TRAUMA CAN DISTORT
THE MEMORY.

07:29.667 --> 07:31.709
[ BEEPING ]

07:35.000 --> 07:37.375
COME ON. I WANT YOU AND RITA
TO MEET MY BOYFRIEND.

07:37.375 --> 07:39.834
IT'S JUST HARD TO GET
A BABYSITTER ON A FRIDAY NIGHT.

07:39.834 --> 07:41.917
DEX, YOU'RE MY BROTHER.
YOU SHOULD KNOW MY BOYFRIEND.

07:41.917 --> 07:44.166
YOU REALLY LIKE USING
THE "B" WORD, DON'T YOU?

07:44.166 --> 07:46.041
WELL, RUDY IS
MY GODDAMN BOYFRIEND,

07:46.041 --> 07:48.417
SO STOP MAKING
BULLSHIT EXCUSES.

07:48.417 --> 07:50.959
HONESTLY, OUR LAST DOUBLE DATE
WAS A LITTLE AWKWARD.

07:50.959 --> 07:54.417
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
THIS ONE'S GONNA STICK.

07:54.417 --> 07:57.750
WELL, THANKS FOR THE VOTE
OF FUCKING CONFIDENCE.

07:57.750 --> 07:59.208
DEX, RUDY'S DIFFERENT.

07:59.208 --> 08:01.208
I FEEL SAFE WITH HIM.

08:01.208 --> 08:04.041
I THINK...
I'M FALLING FOR HIM.

08:04.041 --> 08:07.083
EXCUSE ME.
WHERE CAN I FIND DEXTER MORGAN?

08:07.083 --> 08:08.250
RIGHT HERE.

08:08.250 --> 08:10.834
OH, THAT WAS EASY.

08:12.458 --> 08:15.959
AN URGENT REGISTERED LETTER?
MAYBE YOU WON A SWEEPSTAKES.

08:15.959 --> 08:18.959
DEX, YOU GOT --
YOU GOT A SECOND?

08:18.959 --> 08:20.458
YEAH.

08:23.625 --> 08:25.959
HEY, YOU FINISH YOUR REPORT
ON THE SHOOTING?

08:25.959 --> 08:27.792
I'M WALKING IT UP TO I.A.
RIGHT NOW.

08:27.792 --> 08:30.333
YOU STILL THINK DOAKES' VERSION
DOESN'T ADD UP?

08:30.333 --> 08:32.709
BLOOD NEVER LIES.

08:32.709 --> 08:35.333
SHIT.

08:35.333 --> 08:37.291
LISTEN, UM...

08:37.291 --> 08:39.208
CAN YOU SIT ON THAT
TILL I TALK TO DOAKES?

08:39.208 --> 08:41.166
HERE.

08:41.166 --> 08:43.166
NO, IT'S YOURS
TO SIT ON, STAND ON --

08:43.166 --> 08:44.375
DO WHAT YOU WANT.

08:44.375 --> 08:46.083
THANKS.

08:46.083 --> 08:48.792
YOU'RE WELCOME.

08:48.792 --> 08:51.959
YOU KNOW, IT'S A FEDERAL OFFENSE
TO READ SOMEONE ELSE'S MAIL.

08:51.959 --> 08:54.500
"WE REGRET TO INFORM YOU
OF THE DEATH OF YOUR FATHER"?

08:56.333 --> 08:57.542
DAD DIED 10 YEARS AGO.

08:57.542 --> 08:59.500
THIS ISN'T ABOUT HARRY.

08:59.500 --> 09:01.709
"JOSEPH DRISCOLL
OF DADE CITY, FLORIDA,

09:01.709 --> 09:05.834
NAMES HIS SON, DEXTER MORGAN
OF MIAMI, AS HIS EXECUTOR."

09:05.834 --> 09:07.166
IT'S A WILL.

09:07.166 --> 09:09.166
WELL, HE CAN'T BE
YOUR BIOLOGICAL FATHER.

09:09.166 --> 09:11.750
DAD SAID HE DIED BEFORE YOU CAME
TO LIVE WITH US.

09:11.750 --> 09:13.959
"THE BODY'S
AWAITING CREMATION

09:13.959 --> 09:16.500
WHILE THEY NOTIFY
THE NEXT OF KIN."

09:16.500 --> 09:18.834
I'M YOUR ONLY NEXT OF KIN.
DON'T YOU FUCKING FORGET IT.

09:21.583 --> 09:24.500
OH, AND I INHERITED
A HOUSE.

09:24.500 --> 09:28.000
I KNOW THE TRUTH, BECAUSE HARRY
ALWAYS TOLD ME THE TRUTH.

09:28.000 --> 09:31.083
HE HAD TO. HE WAS TEACHING ME
PRINCIPLES, A CODE.

09:31.083 --> 09:33.542
HE KNEW WHAT I WOULD BECOME
WITHOUT IT.

09:33.542 --> 09:35.667
SO JOSEPH DRISCOLL
OF DADE CITY

09:35.667 --> 09:37.125
MUST HAVE BEEN MISTAKEN.

09:37.125 --> 09:39.583
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

09:40.709 --> 09:43.667
THIS IS DEXTER'S
NEW BIRTH CERTIFICATE.

09:43.667 --> 09:47.000
THE ADOPTION
FINALLY WENT THROUGH.

09:47.000 --> 09:48.875
YOU'RE A MORGAN NOW.

09:48.875 --> 09:50.709
I THOUGHT I WAS
ALREADY A MORGAN.

09:50.709 --> 09:52.750
WELL, YOU HAVE BEEN TO US,
BUT IT'S OFFICIAL NOW.

09:52.750 --> 09:54.750
[ CHUCKLES ]

09:54.750 --> 09:57.375
IT TOOK A LONG TIME
AND A LOT OF HURDLES.

09:57.375 --> 09:59.834
THIS IS
AN IMPORTANT DAY FOR US.

09:59.834 --> 10:01.333
HEY, DAD?

10:01.333 --> 10:02.625
HOW COME YOU NEVER TOLD US

10:02.625 --> 10:05.208
WHAT HAPPENED TO DEXTER'S
REAL PARENTS?

10:05.208 --> 10:06.834
WELL, THEY DIED.

10:06.834 --> 10:08.458
I KNOW, BUT HOW?

10:08.458 --> 10:11.166
I DON'T KNOW.
LET'S NOT TALK ABOUT IT.

10:11.166 --> 10:13.583
NO, HOW DID THEY DIE,
DAD?

10:13.583 --> 10:17.291
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT,
A TRAGIC ACCIDENT.

10:19.834 --> 10:22.208
SO, HAVE YOU FOUND OUT
ANYTHING ELSE

10:22.208 --> 10:23.875
ABOUT THIS JOE DRISCOLL?

10:23.875 --> 10:25.792
WELL, I LOOKED ONLINE.

10:25.792 --> 10:28.667
I EVEN LOOKED
AT POLICE RECORDS.

10:28.667 --> 10:31.291
THERE ARE NO BIRTH RECORDS,
NO DRIVER'S LICENSE,

10:31.291 --> 10:32.959
JUST THE DEED TO THE HOUSE...

10:32.959 --> 10:36.458
AND A MENTION IN THE LOCAL PAPER
ABOUT HIS BOWLING TEAM.

10:36.458 --> 10:37.917
THAT'S ODD.

10:37.917 --> 10:39.583
YEAH, I SPOKE
TO THE PROBATE LAWYER,

10:39.583 --> 10:42.000
THE GUY
WHO DRAFTED THE WILL.

10:42.000 --> 10:44.500
AND APPARENTLY
JOSEPH DRISCOLL

10:44.500 --> 10:47.417
WAS AN INSURANCE ADJUSTER
OF SOUND MIND,

10:47.417 --> 10:49.792
WITH NO DOUBTS
ABOUT WHO I WAS.

10:52.333 --> 10:55.125
DEXTER, YOU'RE NOT FEELING
ANY OF THIS, ARE YOU?

10:55.125 --> 10:59.750
YOU'RE OBVIOUSLY SO OVERWHELMED
THAT YOU'VE SHUT DOWN.

11:04.542 --> 11:06.834
MAYBE.

11:06.834 --> 11:08.583
[ SIGHS ]

11:08.583 --> 11:10.250
IT'S TOO MUCH
FOR YOU TO HANDLE.

11:10.250 --> 11:12.250
YEAH. I GUESS.

11:12.250 --> 11:14.166
SO I THINK I SHOULD COME
WITH YOU.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.750
OH, NO, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO DO THAT.

11:17.750 --> 11:19.625
TRUST ME.
YOU'LL NEED ME.

11:51.250 --> 11:53.417
I FELL ASLEEP.

11:56.333 --> 12:00.250
SEX LIKE THAT TAKES
A LOT OUT OF A PERSON.

12:04.000 --> 12:06.542
[ SMOOCHES ]

12:06.542 --> 12:08.500
SO, ARE WE STILL
SEEING YOUR BROTHER

12:08.500 --> 12:09.667
FOR DINNER FRIDAY NIGHT?

12:09.667 --> 12:12.417
HMM. NO.
HE'S GOT TO GO TO DADE CITY.

12:12.417 --> 12:14.166
WHAT'S IN DADE CITY?

12:14.166 --> 12:16.792
I TOLD YOU
HE WAS ADOPTED, RIGHT?

12:16.792 --> 12:17.792
YEAH.

12:17.792 --> 12:19.750
SOME DEAD GUY
UP IN DADE FUCKING CITY

12:19.750 --> 12:21.542
THOUGHT HE WAS DEXTER'S
BIOLOGICAL FATHER

12:21.542 --> 12:24.208
AND LEFT HIM A HOUSE.

12:24.208 --> 12:25.750
REALLY?

12:25.750 --> 12:27.875
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:27.875 --> 12:29.750
WOW.

12:29.750 --> 12:32.375
MAN.

12:32.375 --> 12:36.625
MMM.
IT'S A MISTAKE, A BIG ONE.

12:36.625 --> 12:39.250
STILL, THOUGH,
THAT'S GOT TO...

12:39.250 --> 12:41.375
OPEN UP SOME OLD WOUNDS.

12:44.375 --> 12:46.125
WHEN ARE YOU LEAVING?

12:46.125 --> 12:48.041
ME?

12:48.041 --> 12:50.709
I'M GONNA STAY IN BED
WITH YOU ALL WEEKEND.

12:50.709 --> 12:53.208
I THOUGHT YOU TWO
WERE CLOSE.

12:53.208 --> 12:56.750
WE ARE.

12:56.750 --> 12:59.041
DEX JUST LIKES TO DEAL
WITH THINGS ON HIS OWN.

12:59.041 --> 13:00.291
HE DOESN'T NEED MY HELP.

13:00.291 --> 13:02.625
OR...

13:02.625 --> 13:05.208
HE DOESN'T KNOW
HOW TO ASK FOR IT.

13:14.041 --> 13:15.458
I LEFT A MESSAGE

13:15.458 --> 13:17.458
SO WE WOULDN'T HAVE
TO HAVE THIS CONVERSATION.

13:17.458 --> 13:19.583
YEAH, WHICH IS
WHY I HUSTLED OVER HERE,

13:19.583 --> 13:21.709
SO WE COULD HASH THIS OUT
LIKE ADULTS.

13:21.709 --> 13:24.583
BUT THIS ADULT IS
STILL GOING OUT OF TOWN.

13:24.583 --> 13:26.083
NOT IF IT MEANS BLOWING OFF

13:26.083 --> 13:28.208
MY SCHEDULED VISIT
WITH MY KIDS.

13:28.208 --> 13:29.750
THAT'S NOT YOUR CALL.

13:29.750 --> 13:31.417
THE KIDS ARE
ALREADY SETTLED AT COLLEEN'S.

13:31.417 --> 13:33.083
YOU CAN HAVE YOUR VISIT
WHEN WE GET BACK.

13:39.375 --> 13:40.917
UH...

13:40.917 --> 13:44.750
IT'S JUST THAT I ALREADY LAID
OUT CASH FOR THE TICKETS.

13:46.250 --> 13:48.458
A DEATH IN THE FAMILY
TRUMPS THE CIRCUS.

13:48.458 --> 13:50.083
DEXTER IS NOT YOUR FAMILY.
I AM.

13:53.500 --> 13:54.917
Dexter: YOU READY?

13:56.750 --> 13:58.583
HEY, PAUL.

13:58.583 --> 14:00.041
BETTER HIT THE ROAD.

14:31.917 --> 14:34.041
[ BURPS ] UGH.

14:34.041 --> 14:35.542
[ SIGHS ]

14:35.542 --> 14:38.542
THEY SHOULD HAVE SERVED A
CARDIOLOGIST WITH THESE BURGERS.

14:38.542 --> 14:40.291
Rita:
WE HAD TO EAT THEM.

14:40.291 --> 14:43.083
JUNK FOOD'S THE UNWRITTEN RULE
OF THE ROAD.

14:43.083 --> 14:45.792
IT'S NICE.

14:45.792 --> 14:47.875
THE LAWYER SAID THERE SHOULD BE
A KEY UNDER THE MAT.

14:52.375 --> 14:55.500
ARE YOU
MY NEW NEIGHBORS?!

14:55.500 --> 14:57.000
NO.

14:57.000 --> 14:58.667
NO, WE'RE JUST HERE
TO CLEAR UP

14:58.667 --> 14:59.667
SOME THINGS
WITH THE ESTATE.

14:59.667 --> 15:01.583
SO SAD ABOUT MR. DRISCOLL.

15:01.583 --> 15:05.667
HE WAS ONLY 60, YOU KNOW --
TOO YOUNG FOR A HEART ATTACK.

15:05.667 --> 15:08.166
HE USED TO CLEAN MY GUTTERS
EVERY FALL.

15:08.166 --> 15:11.667
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M GONNA DO NOW...

15:11.667 --> 15:14.959
UNLESS YOU KNOW
HOW TO CLEAN GUTTERS.

15:14.959 --> 15:17.667
UH, WE'RE NOT GONNA BE HERE
FOR THAT LONG.

15:17.667 --> 15:21.125
BUT, UH,
YOU HAVE A GOOD DAY.

15:25.458 --> 15:27.125
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:33.458 --> 15:36.375
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:39.291 --> 15:41.959
A BACHELOR LIVED HERE,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

15:41.959 --> 15:45.208
[ SIGHS ]

15:45.208 --> 15:47.333
WELL, WE CAN HEAD BACK
TOMORROW MORNING,

15:47.333 --> 15:49.834
AS SOON AS I STRAIGHTEN THINGS
OUT AT THE MORGUE.

15:49.834 --> 15:53.250
I DON'T WANT A HOUSE
IN DADE CITY.

15:53.250 --> 15:55.375
WHICH MEANS IT'S GONNA NEED
TO BE PACKED UP.

15:55.375 --> 15:58.709
AND I DON'T THINK
ANYBODY ELSE IS GONNA DO IT,

15:58.709 --> 16:00.333
SO I GUESS THAT LEAVES US.

16:02.583 --> 16:04.125
TOLD YOU YOU'D NEED ME.

16:30.375 --> 16:31.458
HEY, JAMES.

16:31.458 --> 16:33.125
HEY, MAN.

16:33.125 --> 16:36.250
I.A. IS PRESSING ME
ON MY REPORT OF THE SHOOTING.

16:36.250 --> 16:39.500
YEAH. THERE'S JUST ONE THING
THAT I CAN'T GET CLEAR ON.

16:39.500 --> 16:41.458
IT'S PRETTY CLEAR
FROM WHERE I WAS STANDING.

16:41.458 --> 16:44.250
YEAH...

16:44.250 --> 16:46.083
EXCEPT I COULD HAVE SWORN

16:46.083 --> 16:49.917
THAT I HEARD YOUR 9-MILLIMETER
GO OFF BEFORE THE .38.

16:49.917 --> 16:51.959
NOW, THERE'S LOTS OF REASONS

16:51.959 --> 16:54.125
IT COULD HAVE
GONE DOWN THAT WAY.

16:54.125 --> 16:56.250
IF BAYARD EVEN
JUST AIMED AT YOU,

16:56.250 --> 16:58.291
IT'S STILL ALL RIGHT
TO SHOOT.

16:58.291 --> 17:00.959
EXCEPT HE SHOT FIRST,
WHEN I CAME AROUND THE CORNER.

17:00.959 --> 17:03.375
THE BLOOD-SPATTER REPORT
SAYS IT COULDN'T HAVE
GONE DOWN THAT WAY.

17:03.375 --> 17:05.500
YOU SAYING I'M A LIAR?

17:05.500 --> 17:08.458
NO, I'M SAYING THAT MAYBE YOU'RE
NOT REMEMBERING RIGHT.

17:08.458 --> 17:10.750
THIS MAY COME AS A FUCKING
SHOCK TO YOU, ANGEL,

17:10.750 --> 17:13.208
BUT YOU'RE NOT
THE ONLY HONEST COP IN MIAMI.

17:13.208 --> 17:15.125
[ SIGHS ]

17:15.125 --> 17:18.667
LOOK, I JUST WANT TO KNOW
WHY A MAN IS DEAD.

17:18.667 --> 17:20.625
YOU WANT TO COME AT ME,
YOU COME AT ME STRAIGHT.

17:20.625 --> 17:23.542
YOU WANT IT STRAIGHT?
I DID NOT SEE A GUN.

17:24.959 --> 17:26.208
ANGEL.

17:26.208 --> 17:29.166
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

17:29.166 --> 17:31.166
HELP ME OUT, MAN.

17:45.500 --> 17:47.500
IS THAT JOE?

17:47.500 --> 17:50.000
MUST BE.

17:50.000 --> 17:52.083
HUH.

17:52.083 --> 17:55.500
IT'S WEIRD, BUT HE LOOKS
A LITTLE BIT LIKE YOU...

17:55.500 --> 17:58.166
BUT NOT REALLY.

17:58.166 --> 18:00.667
THOSE SEEM TO BE THE ONLY
PICTURES IN THE HOUSE.

18:00.667 --> 18:05.458
THERE'S NO FAMILY
OR KIDS' PHOTOS.

18:05.458 --> 18:07.625
LONELY.

18:07.625 --> 18:09.542
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

18:16.583 --> 18:17.709
DEXTER.

18:17.709 --> 18:19.625
HI.
HEY.

18:19.625 --> 18:21.250
SURPRISE.

18:21.250 --> 18:23.041
[ LAUGHS ]

18:23.041 --> 18:26.709
I KNOW YOU CAN'T ASK
FOR MY HELP,

18:26.709 --> 18:30.208
BUT IT'S MY DUTY TO,
YOU KNOW...

18:30.208 --> 18:34.583
HELP WHILE YOU DEAL
WITH OLD WOUNDS...

18:34.583 --> 18:36.041
OR WHA-- JESUS.

18:36.041 --> 18:37.542
WHATEVER. I'M HERE.

18:37.542 --> 18:38.875
SO IT APPEARS.

18:38.875 --> 18:41.166
MM-HMM,
AND THIS IS RUDY.

18:41.166 --> 18:42.417
HEY.

18:45.041 --> 18:47.083
I'VE WAITED A LONG TIME
TO MEET YOU.

18:48.875 --> 18:52.000
AND YOU MUST BE RITA.

18:52.000 --> 18:53.417
HI.
HI.

18:53.417 --> 18:57.792
HE CAME HERE FOR ME --
FOR THE BOTH OF US.

18:57.792 --> 19:00.250
ISN'T HE GREAT?

19:07.750 --> 19:10.125
A LOT OF WORK
TO PACK ALL THIS UP.

19:10.125 --> 19:13.250
EVEN WITH THE FOUR OF US,
IT'LL TAKE US THE WHOLE WEEKEND.

19:13.250 --> 19:14.542
THE WHOLE WEEKEND?

19:14.542 --> 19:15.500
WHERE SHOULD I PUT
OUR STUFF?

19:15.500 --> 19:17.625
[ GROANS ]

19:17.625 --> 19:20.709
IT'S TOO EERIE,
SLEEPING IN A DEAD MAN'S HOUSE.

19:20.709 --> 19:22.583
I SAW A MOTEL 6
ON THE WAY IN.

19:22.583 --> 19:24.750
WE COULD STAY HERE
AND SAVE THE MONEY.

19:24.750 --> 19:26.667
Rita: I MEAN, IT IS LATE,

19:26.667 --> 19:29.083
AND WE'D PROBABLY GET MORE
PACKING DONE IF WE STAYED HERE.

19:29.083 --> 19:32.291
IT'S UP TO YOU, DEX.
JUST SAY THE WORD.

19:35.000 --> 19:37.208
AS LONG AS YOU DON'T MIND
THE SOFA BED.

19:38.792 --> 19:41.250
OKAY, I'LL GO LOOK
FOR SOME CLEAN SHEETS.

19:41.250 --> 19:43.333
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

19:49.417 --> 19:52.125
HOW DID A DEATH
TURN INTO A COUPLES' WEEKEND?

19:58.458 --> 20:01.375
LUCKILY, I GET UP
EARLIER THAN NORMAL PEOPLE.

20:01.375 --> 20:02.959
Rudy: COFFEE?

20:04.166 --> 20:06.959
[ SIGHS ] THANKS.

20:06.959 --> 20:08.959
I'VE GOT TO HIT
THE MORGUE.

20:12.250 --> 20:14.500
WANT COMPANY?

20:14.500 --> 20:16.583
[ SIGHS ] NO.

20:16.583 --> 20:18.875
THANK YOU, THOUGH.

20:18.875 --> 20:20.875
IT'S PRIVATE.

20:20.875 --> 20:22.709
I GET IT.

20:22.709 --> 20:24.750
[ SIGHS ]

20:32.291 --> 20:35.709
I GAVE JOE A PHYSICAL
ONCE A YEAR, LIKE CLOCKWORK,

20:35.709 --> 20:38.792
SO NO HISTORY OF HEART DISEASE,
BUT IT HAPPENS.

20:38.792 --> 20:40.333
IT APPEARS SO.

20:40.333 --> 20:42.625
WE WERE ABOUT TO SEND HIM
TO A CREMATORIUM.

20:42.625 --> 20:45.834
WE THOUGHT HIS SON
SHOULD HAVE A CHANCE

20:45.834 --> 20:47.667
TO PAY HIS LAST RESPECTS.

20:47.667 --> 20:49.709
I'M NOT HIS SON.

20:49.709 --> 20:52.709
ESTRANGEMENT IN A FAMILY
IS A SHAME,

20:52.709 --> 20:55.875
BUT DEATH IS
THE GREAT UNIFIER.

21:34.125 --> 21:36.417
HUH. THAT'S
AN INTERESTING TATTOO.

21:36.417 --> 21:39.166
JOE SAID HE PICKED
THAT UP IN NAM.

21:39.166 --> 21:41.583
YOU CAN BE PROUD.
HE WAS A PATRIOT.

21:41.583 --> 21:44.250
UH, PERHAPS HE WAS
ALSO AN EX-CONVICT.

21:44.250 --> 21:45.792
EXCUSE ME?

21:45.792 --> 21:47.333
IT'S A PRISON TATTOO.

21:47.333 --> 21:50.041
IT'S DONE WITH A PEN
AND BALLPOINT INK.

21:50.041 --> 21:54.000
IT'S THREE OR FOUR DECADES OLD,
JUDGING BY THE FADE.

21:54.000 --> 21:56.208
SON, I KNEW JOE.
HE WAS NO EX-CONVICT.

21:56.208 --> 21:59.041
HE WAS A GOOD MAN,
A QUIET MAN,

21:59.041 --> 22:01.417
AND A DAMN GOOD BOWLER.

22:04.000 --> 22:06.041
HOW'D YOU DETERMINE
CARDIAC ARREST?

22:06.041 --> 22:08.291
WAS THERE DAMAGE
TO THE CORONARY ARTERY?

22:08.291 --> 22:11.250
IT'S, UH,
PROFESSIONAL CURIOSITY.

22:11.250 --> 22:13.917
I WORK IN FORENSICS,
DOWN IN MIAMI.

22:13.917 --> 22:15.709
I SEE.

22:15.709 --> 22:20.000
WELL, UH, I FOUND MICROANEURISMS
IN THE RETINAS.

22:20.000 --> 22:22.959
IT'S COMMON WITH SEIZURES
DURING A HEART ATTACK.

22:22.959 --> 22:26.250
IT'S ALSO A SIGN
OF DIABETIC RETINOPATHY.

22:26.250 --> 22:29.291
SON, I MAY BE
A SMALL-TOWN DOCTOR,

22:29.291 --> 22:33.041
BUT I KNOW A HEART ATTACK
WHEN I SEE ONE.

22:33.041 --> 22:35.125
WHO KNOWS WHAT CAUSED IT --

22:35.125 --> 22:39.625
STRESS, INACTIVITY...

22:39.625 --> 22:42.000
FRENCH FRIES --

22:42.000 --> 22:44.959
BUT KNOWING
WON'T BRING HIM BACK.

22:46.959 --> 22:50.000
♪ I WANNA KNOW ♪

22:50.000 --> 22:55.458
♪ HAVE YOU EVER SEEN THE RAIN? ♪

22:55.458 --> 22:57.458
♪ COMING DOWN ♪

22:57.458 --> 23:00.041
IT'S HARD TO ACCEPT
SO MANY UNANSWERED QUESTIONS,

23:00.041 --> 23:01.542
BUT SOMETIMES...

23:01.542 --> 23:04.625
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT...

23:04.625 --> 23:06.875
DR. PITTMAN.

23:06.875 --> 23:09.667
[ SIGHS ]
YEAH, THIS IS REALLY HARD.

23:12.000 --> 23:15.625
YOU MIND IF I JUST TAKE
A MINUTE ALONE WITH...

23:15.625 --> 23:17.333
DAD?

23:17.333 --> 23:20.417
I'LL BE NEXT DOOR
IN MY OFFICE.

23:23.500 --> 23:25.417
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:46.083 --> 23:48.750
[ Telephone rings ]

23:48.750 --> 23:50.250
Masuka.

23:50.250 --> 23:52.125
HEY, IT'S DEXTER MORGAN.

23:52.125 --> 23:54.208
DUDE,
I KNOW YOUR LAST NAME.

23:54.208 --> 23:56.625
I need a favor,
a DNA comparison.

23:56.625 --> 23:59.125
I THOUGHT YOU WERE AWAY
WITH THE GIRLFRIEND.

23:59.125 --> 24:01.083
WHAT? SHE SURFING
THE CRIMSON WAVE?

24:01.083 --> 24:03.792
I'M JUST HELPING OUT
A LOCAL AGENCY.

24:03.792 --> 24:06.750
I'M GONNA SEND YOU
TWO BLOOD SAMPLES.

24:06.750 --> 24:08.208
I NEED IT A.S.A.P.

24:08.208 --> 24:09.709
DO A TOX SCREEN, WILL YOU?

24:09.709 --> 24:13.000
HEY, ROMEO, IF THIS IS YOUR IDEA
OF A ROMANTIC WEEKEND,

24:13.000 --> 24:15.166
YOU'RE GONNA BE A BACHELOR
FOR A VERY LONG TIME.

24:15.166 --> 24:16.208
YEAH.

24:16.208 --> 24:17.417
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

24:25.083 --> 24:26.750
Man: RUN ANOTHER I.V.

24:26.750 --> 24:28.291
LET'S KEEP
HIS BLOOD LEVELS VOLUMIZED.

24:28.291 --> 24:29.834
Man #2:
WHAT'S HIS PRESSURE?

24:29.834 --> 24:31.250
Woman:
IT'S 80 AND DROPPING.

24:31.250 --> 24:33.166
WE MAY NEED
TO DO A BELLY TAP.

24:33.166 --> 24:36.291
HEY, DEX.
BUDDY, I'M HERE.

24:36.291 --> 24:38.458
IT HURTS, DAD.
WHAT HAPPENED?

24:38.458 --> 24:41.333
HE TRIED TO CLIMB A FENCE
TO GET DEBRA'S BALL,

24:41.333 --> 24:42.834
BUT A DOG CHASED AFTER HIM,

24:42.834 --> 24:45.208
AND HE FELL
ON A WROUGHT-IRON POST.

24:45.208 --> 24:46.750
IS HE GONNA BE ALL RIGHT?

24:46.750 --> 24:48.542
WE CAN KEEP HIM STABLE
FOR A WHILE.

24:48.542 --> 24:50.625
BUT HE'S GONNA NEED SURGERY TO
REPAIR SOME INTERNAL BLEEDING,

24:50.625 --> 24:51.917
AND THAT'S A PROBLEM.

24:51.917 --> 24:53.250
CAN WE TALK
OVER HERE, PLEASE?

24:53.250 --> 24:55.417
DEX,
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

24:55.417 --> 24:57.667
HOLD YOUR BROTHER'S HAND,
SWEETIE.

24:57.667 --> 25:01.333
OKAY, THE COMPLICATION IS
WITH YOUR SON'S BLOOD TYPE.

25:01.333 --> 25:03.458
I don't want
to talk about this.

25:03.458 --> 25:05.166
Why are you being
like this?!

25:05.166 --> 25:07.000
You don't need to mention
that in front of anybody.

25:07.000 --> 25:08.709
Are you crazy?!

25:08.709 --> 25:11.458
He could die.
You've got to go now.

25:15.959 --> 25:17.458
SO, YOU HEARD
THE .38 GO OFF

25:17.458 --> 25:19.667
BEFORE SERGEANT DOAKES'
9-MILLIMETER.

25:19.667 --> 25:22.083
THEN I WENT UNDER THE CAUSEWAY,
AND I SAW THE SUSPECT...

25:22.083 --> 25:23.208
MR. BAYARD.

25:23.208 --> 25:27.041
...MR. BAYARD
ON THE GROUND,

25:27.041 --> 25:28.500
HIS GUN LYING NEXT TO HIM.

25:28.500 --> 25:30.250
AND YOU'RE SURE
IT WAS MR. BAYARD'S GUN?

25:30.250 --> 25:32.750
WELL,
THE .38 WASN'T MINE.

25:32.750 --> 25:34.834
AND SERGEANT DOAKES
HAD HIS NINER IN HIS HANDS.

25:34.834 --> 25:36.959
DID YOU SEE MR. BAYARD
CARRYING THE GUN

25:36.959 --> 25:38.166
BEFORE THE FOOT CHASE BEGAN?

25:38.166 --> 25:40.750
SERGEANT DOAKES DID.

25:40.750 --> 25:42.625
DID YOU SEE MR. BAYARD
ACTING SUSPICIOUSLY?

25:44.750 --> 25:47.000
DID YOU KNOW MR. BAYARD
WORKED AS A JANITOR?

25:47.000 --> 25:49.542
I -- HOW THE FUCK
WOULD I KNOW THAT?

25:49.542 --> 25:51.667
NEVER GOT SO MUCH
AS A PARKING TICKET

25:51.667 --> 25:53.917
SINCE HE IMMIGRATED FROM HAITI
15 YEARS AGO.

25:57.083 --> 26:00.750
HE GOT A LOT MORE THAN THAT
THIS TIME, DIDN'T HE?

26:06.583 --> 26:08.458
ARE YOU SURE YOU HEARD
THE .38 GO OFF

26:08.458 --> 26:11.000
BEFORE SERGEANT DOAKES'
9-MILLIMETER?

26:21.000 --> 26:24.333
JOE BOUGHT THIS HOUSE
OUTRIGHT IN 1976,

26:24.333 --> 26:27.583
PAID CASH,
NO RECORDS BEFORE THAT.

26:27.583 --> 26:31.041
NO RECORDS,
NO CHILDHOOD PHOTOS...

26:31.041 --> 26:32.542
THE GUY WAS 60,

26:32.542 --> 26:34.583
BUT IT'S LIKE HIS LIFE
STARTED WHEN HE WAS 30.

26:34.583 --> 26:38.542
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE RIGHT.
HE'S RIGHT.

26:38.542 --> 26:40.500
SO, WHAT HAPPENED
BETWEEN YEARS ONE AND 29?

26:40.500 --> 26:43.625
MAYBE HE BUTCHERED
HIS ENTIRE FAMILY.

26:43.625 --> 26:45.792
YEAH, OR HE WALKED OUT
ON HIS TWO WIVES

26:45.792 --> 26:47.875
AND A LOT OF BAD DEBT.

26:47.875 --> 26:49.750
THE GUY WAS A LOSER,
AFTER ALL.

26:49.750 --> 26:51.500
WHO ELSE OWNS
THIS MANY BOWLING BALLS?

26:51.500 --> 26:53.583
WHAT DO YOU THINK, DEX?

26:53.583 --> 26:58.166
I THINK JOE SPENT
SOME TIME IN PRISON,

26:58.166 --> 27:00.291
PROBABLY MIXED
WITH SOME BAD PEOPLE.

27:00.291 --> 27:02.083
MAYBE HE HAD
TO HIDE FROM THEM.

27:02.083 --> 27:04.542
WHATEVER IT WAS,
DRUGS WERE INVOLVED --

27:04.542 --> 27:06.250
NARCOTICS ANONYMOUS.

27:06.250 --> 27:07.667
PAUL USED TO GET THESE,

27:07.667 --> 27:10.542
EXCEPT HE NEVER MADE IT
PAST THE WELCOME CHIP.

27:10.542 --> 27:13.375
LOOKS LIKE JOE
WAS CLEAN FOR...

27:13.375 --> 27:14.875
LET ME GUESS -- 30 YEARS.

27:14.875 --> 27:16.458
Rudy: WELL, JOE SAID NO
TO THE DRUGS,

27:16.458 --> 27:17.875
BUT NOT HIS ROCK 'N' ROLL.

27:17.875 --> 27:20.917
NOTHING IN HIS COLLECTION
POST-1980.

27:20.917 --> 27:22.542
GOT TO LOVE A PURIST.

27:22.542 --> 27:24.750
[ FOGHAT'S "SLOW RIDE" PLAYS ]

27:29.083 --> 27:30.709
♪ WHOO ♪

27:30.709 --> 27:34.291
♪ OHH ♪

27:34.291 --> 27:37.917
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

27:37.917 --> 27:40.333
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

27:40.333 --> 27:41.709
OH, GOOD. DANCING.

27:41.709 --> 27:46.083
♪ TAKE IT EASY ♪

27:46.083 --> 27:49.625
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

27:49.625 --> 27:54.291
♪ TAKE IT EASY ♪

27:54.291 --> 27:57.917
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

27:57.917 --> 28:02.417
♪ TAKE IT EASY ♪

28:02.417 --> 28:06.458
♪ I'M IN THE MOOD ♪

28:06.458 --> 28:10.709
♪ THE RHYTHM IS RIGHT ♪

28:10.709 --> 28:14.625
♪ MOVE TO THE MUSIC ♪

28:14.625 --> 28:19.291
♪ WE CAN ROLL ALL NIGHT ♪

28:19.291 --> 28:23.458
♪ OOOH, OOOH ♪

28:23.458 --> 28:27.625
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

28:27.625 --> 28:31.834
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
♪ OOOH, OOOH ♪

28:31.834 --> 28:33.041
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

28:33.041 --> 28:34.417
HELLO?

28:34.417 --> 28:36.834
Hey, babe.
It's Paul.

28:39.542 --> 28:41.834
JUST MAKING SURE
DEAR DEXTER

28:41.834 --> 28:45.000
IS DEALING DECENTLY
WITH HIS DEAD DAD.

28:45.000 --> 28:46.208
[ LAUGHS ]

28:46.208 --> 28:47.583
♪ SLOW RIDE ♪

28:47.583 --> 28:49.834
WE'RE FINE.
EVERYONE'S FINE, ALL RIGHT?

28:49.834 --> 28:51.333
WE'LL SEE YOU ON MONDAY.

28:51.333 --> 28:52.458
No, no, no.

28:52.458 --> 28:55.375
Talk to me.
You having fun?

28:55.375 --> 28:56.667
'Cause I'm not.

28:56.667 --> 28:57.709
PAUL.

28:57.709 --> 28:59.834
I WOULD HAVE.

28:59.834 --> 29:02.458
I COULD HAVE TAKEN
MY KIDS TO THE CIRCUS.

29:02.458 --> 29:04.000
[ Scoffs ]

29:04.000 --> 29:07.125
WE'D BE EATING PEANUTS
RIGHT NOW,

29:07.125 --> 29:08.875
STEPPING IN ELEPHANT SHIT.

29:08.875 --> 29:11.083
PAUL, THIS IS NOT HELPING
MY CONFIDENCE IN YOU.

29:11.083 --> 29:15.000
OH, I THINK YOU'VE GOT ENOUGH
CONFIDENCE FOR BOTH OF US.

29:15.000 --> 29:16.709
LOOK, IF YOU WANT TO WORK

29:16.709 --> 29:18.333
TOWARDS BUILDING
MORE VISITATION DAYS, NOT LESS,

29:18.333 --> 29:20.625
YOU NEED TO AVOID THIS
KIND OF BEHAVIOR RIGHT HERE.

29:20.625 --> 29:22.291
[ SNIFFLES ]

29:25.000 --> 29:28.917
Now, I think you might just want
to politely hang up.

29:33.041 --> 29:34.166
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

29:34.166 --> 29:36.542
OKAY.

29:36.542 --> 29:38.875
YOU'RE RIGHT.

29:38.875 --> 29:41.667
I'M SORRY.

29:41.667 --> 29:43.417
YOU HAVE A GREAT WEEKEND.

29:46.667 --> 29:48.083
[ RECEIVER CLICKS ]

29:48.083 --> 29:49.917
[ SIGHS ]

29:54.375 --> 29:58.375
A SECRET LIFE -- THE ONLY THING
JOE AND I HAVE IN COMMON.

29:58.375 --> 30:01.875
THERE'S NOTHING ELSE
IN THIS HOUSE TO CONNECT US.

30:01.875 --> 30:03.959
HIDING OUT?

30:06.792 --> 30:08.250
CLEANING UP.

30:08.250 --> 30:10.250
[ DISHES RATTLE ]

30:12.000 --> 30:14.709
I CAN ONLY IMAGINE
WHAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

30:14.709 --> 30:18.291
A LOT OF LEMON-FRESH JOY.

30:18.291 --> 30:19.750
YOU JOKE.

30:19.750 --> 30:22.083
IT'S GOOD DEFENSE,
BY THE WAY.

30:22.083 --> 30:23.667
THANK YOU, I THINK.

30:23.667 --> 30:27.417
STILL, THE POSSIBILITY HAS
GOT TO BE WEIGHING ON YOU.

30:27.417 --> 30:28.917
WHAT POSSIBILITY?

30:28.917 --> 30:32.208
THAT JOE COULD
ACTUALLY BE YOUR DAD.

30:32.208 --> 30:34.250
THE ONLY WAY
THAT'S A POSSIBILITY

30:34.250 --> 30:36.000
IS IF HARRY WAS WRONG.

30:36.000 --> 30:40.166
AND, UH, THAT'S
JUST NOT POSSIBLE.

30:40.166 --> 30:42.125
OR HE LIED.

30:44.250 --> 30:45.792
Man: DON'T YOU WORRY,
LITTLE MAN.

30:45.792 --> 30:47.583
YOU'RE NOT GONNA FEEL
A THING.

30:47.583 --> 30:50.291
I THOUGHT THERE WAS A PROBLEM --
YOU KNOW, THE BLOOD?

30:50.291 --> 30:51.667
YOUR DAD FIXED IT.

30:51.667 --> 30:54.959
SEE, YOU HAVE A VERY SPECIAL
BLOOD TYPE -- A.B. NEGATIVE.

30:54.959 --> 30:57.208
IT'S HARD TO COME BY,
AND OUR SUPPLY WAS LOW.

30:57.208 --> 30:59.458
BUT YOUR DAD KNEW SOMEBODY
WITH BLOOD JUST LIKE YOURS.

30:59.458 --> 31:00.834
YOU'RE VERY LUCKY.

31:00.834 --> 31:02.291
CAN I HAVE A MOMENT
WITH MY SON?

31:02.291 --> 31:03.500
YEAH.

31:03.500 --> 31:05.125
HEY, DEX.

31:05.125 --> 31:08.375
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE FINE.
YOU'LL BE GOOD AS NEW.

31:08.375 --> 31:10.250
I WILL?

31:10.250 --> 31:11.625
HEY, WOULD I LIE TO YOU?

31:16.458 --> 31:18.458
Angel:
WHEN MY FATHER WAS DYING,

31:18.458 --> 31:20.458
HE JUST ASKED ME
FOR ONE THING --

31:20.458 --> 31:23.375
DEBERíA SER
UN HOMBRE HONESTO.

31:27.375 --> 31:29.166
"BE AN HONEST MAN."

31:32.583 --> 31:34.667
THAT'S ALL HE ASKED.

31:37.041 --> 31:40.667
I MADE HIM THAT PROMISE,
AND THAT'S WHY I'M A COP.

31:45.375 --> 31:48.000
NOW THIS HAITIAN MAN IS DEAD,

31:48.000 --> 31:51.000
AND I DON'T KNOW WHY,

31:51.000 --> 31:52.917
BUT I KNOW IT AIN'T RIGHT.

31:56.000 --> 31:58.375
BUT IF I TALK...

31:58.375 --> 32:00.959
I'LL BE A RAT
TO THE WHOLE PRECINCT.

32:00.959 --> 32:02.834
[ TAPE RECORDER CLICKS ]

32:02.834 --> 32:04.291
BUT IF I LIE --

32:04.291 --> 32:05.375
HOLD UP.

32:11.959 --> 32:14.125
[ SIGHS ]

32:15.959 --> 32:18.125
GO AHEAD.

32:31.583 --> 32:35.125
THE BLOOD SPATTER
DOESN'T MATCH DOAKES' REPORT.

32:39.417 --> 32:40.625
ALSO...

32:44.458 --> 32:48.000
...I HEARD DOAKES' 9-MILLIMETER
GO OFF BEFORE THE .38.

32:48.000 --> 32:50.208
BUT HE MUST
HAVE HAD GOOD CAUSE.

32:50.208 --> 32:52.250
SO DOAKES FIRED FIRST.

32:58.208 --> 33:00.417
DOAKES FIRED FIRST.

33:02.542 --> 33:04.166
[ TAPE RECORDER CLICKS ]

33:11.917 --> 33:13.917
I HOPE TUNA'S ALL RIGHT.

33:13.917 --> 33:16.083
MMM,
LOVE ME A LITTLE MERCURY.

33:16.083 --> 33:18.291
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
THAT'S DEXTER'S.

33:18.291 --> 33:20.375
OH, HE'S OUT STEALING
GARBAGE-CAN SPACE

33:20.375 --> 33:21.667
FROM THE NEIGHBORS.

33:21.667 --> 33:23.583
CRIMINAL -- I LIKE IT.

33:23.583 --> 33:25.542
MMM, IT'S THE STATION.

33:25.542 --> 33:26.542
MORGAN HERE.

33:28.125 --> 33:31.625
WAIT. DID I CALL
THE HOT MORGAN BY MISTAKE?

33:31.625 --> 33:33.792
FREUDIAN.

33:33.792 --> 33:35.500
MY SUBCONSCIOUS
HAS BEEN EXPOSED.

33:35.500 --> 33:37.041
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:37.041 --> 33:38.625
WELL, ZIP IT UP AND TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON.

33:38.625 --> 33:39.959
I got the results.

33:39.959 --> 33:41.834
ON DOAKES' SHOOTING?
HAS HE BEEN CLEARED?

33:41.834 --> 33:43.583
ON THE DNA TEST.

33:43.583 --> 33:46.041
WHAT DNA TEST?

34:03.333 --> 34:06.291
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

34:06.291 --> 34:09.208
YOU TRUSTED DAD YOUR ENTIRE
LIFE, SO WHY QUESTION HIM NOW?

34:12.000 --> 34:13.500
AM I MISSING SOMETHING?

34:15.375 --> 34:17.875
DNA TEST?

34:17.875 --> 34:20.709
[ SIGHS ]
MASUKA CALLED?

34:20.709 --> 34:22.834
YOUR BIOLOGICAL FATHER
WAS DEAD.

34:22.834 --> 34:25.500
DAD TOLD US THAT.
I REMEMBER.

34:25.500 --> 34:27.333
SO, THE DNA
CAME BACK NEGATIVE?

34:29.875 --> 34:31.667
IT WAS A MATCH.

34:33.458 --> 34:36.667
JOE DRISCOLL
WAS YOUR BIO DAD.

34:48.041 --> 34:49.250
INTERESTING.

34:51.166 --> 34:53.500
DO YOU THINK DAD...

34:53.500 --> 34:55.375
LIED?

34:55.375 --> 34:58.625
I THINK HE MIGHT HAVE KNOWN
JOE WAS HERE...

35:01.208 --> 35:03.792
...FIVE HOURS UP I-95
MY WHOLE LIFE.

35:03.792 --> 35:06.333
WELL, HE MUST HAVE HAD
A DAMN GOOD REASON.

35:06.333 --> 35:09.166
AND I'M NOT GONNA LET
SOME GUY YOU DIDN'T EVEN KNOW

35:09.166 --> 35:11.041
DRAW HIM INTO QUESTION.

35:11.041 --> 35:13.041
DEB, I'M NOT
QUESTIONING ANYTHING.

35:13.041 --> 35:16.709
THAT'S WHY YOU GOT
A TOX SCREEN, TOO.

35:18.500 --> 35:19.917
[ DOOR OPENS ]

35:21.750 --> 35:23.417
I NEED TO CLEAR MY HEAD.

35:25.333 --> 35:27.875
WHERE ARE YOUR CAR KEYS?

35:32.125 --> 35:33.917
DEB, I ORDERED
THE TOX SCREEN

35:33.917 --> 35:35.709
BECAUSE JOE HAD NO HISTORY
OF HEART DISEASE

35:35.709 --> 35:37.709
AND THE CORONER'S REPORT
WAS INEPT.

35:37.709 --> 35:39.041
YOU DID IT

35:39.041 --> 35:40.709
BECAUSE, FOR SOME REASON,
HE IS IMPORTANT TO YOU.

35:40.709 --> 35:42.333
IT WAS
PROFESSIONAL CURIOSITY.

35:42.333 --> 35:44.542
THEN YOU WILL BE
PROFESSIONALLY GLAD TO KNOW

35:44.542 --> 35:46.792
THAT THE ONLY TOXIN
IN HIS SYSTEM WAS A SEDATIVE,

35:46.792 --> 35:48.792
WHICH HE PROBABLY TOOK TO...

35:48.792 --> 35:50.917
I DON'T KNOW, SLEEP.

35:50.917 --> 35:53.250
Rita:
THAT WOULD SURPRISE ME.

35:53.250 --> 35:55.750
JOE WAS 30 YEARS SOBER,
AND I HAVEN'T FOUND ANYTHING

35:55.750 --> 35:58.083
STRONGER THAN ADVIL
IN HIS MEDICINE CABINET.

36:00.000 --> 36:01.917
IT WOULDN'T BE
THE FIRST TIME

36:01.917 --> 36:03.417
AN ADDICT
FELL OFF THE WAGON, RITA.

36:03.417 --> 36:05.875
OR SOMEONE SLIPPED HIM
THE SEDATIVE

36:05.875 --> 36:08.417
SO HE WOULDN'T STRUGGLE WHEN
HE WAS INJECTED WITH SOMETHING.

36:08.417 --> 36:09.792
LIKE?

36:09.792 --> 36:11.208
DIABETIC INSULIN.

36:12.291 --> 36:13.875
IT CAN CAUSE CARDIAC ARREST.

36:13.875 --> 36:15.417
WE'VE SEEN IT BEFORE.

36:15.417 --> 36:17.291
IT'S NEARLY IMPOSSIBLE
TO DETECT

36:17.291 --> 36:18.792
UNLESS YOU CAN FIND
A POINT OF INJECTION,

36:18.792 --> 36:20.625
WHICH I WASN'T LOOKING FOR,
BUT IF I HAD A CHANCE --

36:20.625 --> 36:22.458
Debra: JESUS CHRIST!

36:22.458 --> 36:24.333
HE'S NOT EVEN YOUR FAMILY.

36:25.917 --> 36:29.333
MOM AND DAD WERE. I AM.

36:32.083 --> 36:34.583
ARE YOU GONNA START
QUESTIONING ME NOW?

36:34.583 --> 36:36.709
YOU? WHY WOULD I --

36:36.709 --> 36:39.542
JOE DRISCOLL WAS
OBVIOUSLY BAD FUCKING NEWS,

36:39.542 --> 36:42.583
WHICH IS WHY DAD DIDN'T WANT YOU
TO KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT HIM!

36:42.583 --> 36:44.375
DOESN'T THAT MATTER
TO YOU?!

36:44.375 --> 36:47.625
UH...[ SIGHS ]

36:47.625 --> 36:49.500
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU WANT FROM ME.

36:55.500 --> 36:58.208
I WANT WHAT DAD WANTED.

36:58.208 --> 37:00.333
I WANT NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS GUY.

37:00.333 --> 37:03.792
LET'S JUST FINISH PACKING UP
THIS CRAPPY HOUSE

37:03.792 --> 37:06.458
AND WALK THE FUCK AWAY!

37:06.458 --> 37:08.834
ALL RIGHT. THAT SOUNDS
LIKE A GOOD PLAN. OKAY?

37:25.500 --> 37:28.083
I GUESS I UNDERSTAND
WHY DEB IS UPSET.

37:28.083 --> 37:31.375
WE BOTH IDOLIZED HARRY,
LIVED BY WHAT HE TAUGHT US...

37:31.375 --> 37:33.834
THOUGH DEB NEVER HAD
TO BE TAUGHT

37:33.834 --> 37:35.875
NOT TO KILL INNOCENT PEOPLE.

37:35.875 --> 37:38.458
[ DOOR OPENS IN DISTANCE ]

37:38.458 --> 37:41.291
THAT'S WHY SHE DOESN'T
UNDERSTAND WHY I NEED TO KNOW.

37:47.208 --> 37:49.625
HOWDY, NEIGHBOR.
LET ME GET THAT FOR YOU.

37:49.625 --> 37:52.417
OH.
WELL, THANK YOU.

37:52.417 --> 37:54.625
I WAS JUST WONDERING --
DID YOU HAPPEN TO NOTICE

37:54.625 --> 37:56.208
ANY VISITORS
OVER AT JOE'S LAST WEEK?

37:56.208 --> 37:59.500
VISITORS?
OH, I'M NOT SURE.

37:59.500 --> 38:03.208
I'M JUST WONDERING IF HE HAS
ANY OUTSTANDING BILLS --

38:03.208 --> 38:06.709
A GARDENER, MAYBE,
OR A DELIVERY PERSON, REPAIRMAN?

38:06.709 --> 38:08.500
WELL, COME TO THINK OF IT,

38:08.500 --> 38:12.291
THERE WAS A, UM, CABLE REPAIRMAN
HERE LAST WEEK.

38:12.291 --> 38:14.500
HE WAS POLITE.

38:14.500 --> 38:17.750
BUT, YOU KNOW, HE COULDN'T
FIX MY TV ANTENNA.

38:17.750 --> 38:20.000
YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HE LOOKED LIKE?

38:20.000 --> 38:21.917
OH.
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

38:21.917 --> 38:25.041
WELL, HE HAD DARK HAIR...

38:25.041 --> 38:28.917
AVERAGE HEIGHT --
NORMAL, I SUPPOSE.

38:32.333 --> 38:35.291
I DID SOME CHECKING
ON OUR SUSPECT JACQUES BAYARD.

38:35.291 --> 38:38.041
YOU LENDING I.A. A HAND?

38:38.041 --> 38:40.625
I JUST LIKE TO KNOW WHAT'S
GOING ON IN MY DEPARTMENT.

38:40.625 --> 38:42.917
AND WHAT IS GOING ON?

38:42.917 --> 38:44.583
TURNS OUT MR. BAYARD

38:44.583 --> 38:47.750
CHANGED HIS NAME
WHEN HE IMMIGRATED HERE.

38:47.750 --> 38:49.542
USED TO BE RENE THIBAULT,

38:49.542 --> 38:52.917
A FORMER OFFICER
IN THE HAITIAN MILITARY.

38:52.917 --> 38:55.208
DIDN'T YOUR TOUR IN THE ARMY

38:55.208 --> 38:58.500
INCLUDE SOME SPECIAL OP
IN HAITI?

39:00.291 --> 39:01.458
RIGHT.

39:01.458 --> 39:03.542
"SPECIAL" MEANS
YOU DON'T TALK ABOUT IT.

39:03.542 --> 39:07.208
BUT I KNOW YOU'VE HEARD
AS MANY HORROR STORIES AS I HAVE

39:07.208 --> 39:10.834
ABOUT WHAT WENT ON DOWN THERE
WITH THOSE DEATH SQUADS.

39:10.834 --> 39:12.750
WHAT WERE THEY CALLED?

39:12.750 --> 39:15.959
TONTON MACOUTES.

39:15.959 --> 39:18.875
YEAH, "THE BOGEYMEN."

39:21.125 --> 39:23.583
THEY DID A LOT
OF TERRIBLE THINGS,

39:23.583 --> 39:26.041
KILLED A LOT OF PEOPLE.

39:29.291 --> 39:33.166
THEY MADE MOTHERS CARRY
THE HEADS OF THEIR DEAD SONS,

39:33.166 --> 39:35.500
FORCED FATHERS TO RAPE
THEIR DAUGHTERS.

39:35.500 --> 39:38.959
THEY TIED CINDER BLOCKS AROUND
PEOPLE'S NECKS AND DROWNED THEM

39:38.959 --> 39:41.000
AND PUT MUTILATED BODIES
IN TREES

39:41.000 --> 39:43.709
AND KILLED ANYBODY WHO TRIED
TO TAKE THEM DOWN.

39:47.041 --> 39:50.458
THIS MAN, JACQUES BAYARD,

39:50.458 --> 39:53.291
IF HE DID THOSE THINGS...

39:53.291 --> 39:55.542
HE DESERVED A LOT WORSE
THAN HE GOT.

40:02.709 --> 40:04.792
DON'T WORRY, JAMES.

40:04.792 --> 40:06.834
IT'LL BE OVER SOON.

40:10.667 --> 40:12.542
I KNOW IT WILL.

40:25.542 --> 40:27.625
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

40:31.333 --> 40:34.041
IF JOE WAS SHOT UP
WITH INSULIN,

40:34.041 --> 40:36.375
THERE WILL BE
AN INJECTION WELT...

40:36.375 --> 40:39.417
MAYBE BETWEEN HIS TOES
OR IN A FRECKLE.

40:39.417 --> 40:41.083
IF IT'S THERE, I'LL FIND IT.

40:45.959 --> 40:48.250
SMALL TOWNS.

41:11.208 --> 41:13.583
COME ON, DR. PITTMAN,

41:13.583 --> 41:17.500
WHICH CREMATORIUM
DID YOU SEND JOE TO?

41:31.542 --> 41:32.792
[ HINGES CREAK ]

41:32.792 --> 41:34.625
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

41:34.625 --> 41:36.792
HEY! YOU! STOP!

41:36.792 --> 41:38.250
COME ON!

41:58.125 --> 41:59.792
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

41:59.792 --> 42:01.291
Rudy: GET IN!

42:09.333 --> 42:11.375
HEARD YOU SNEAK OUT.

42:11.375 --> 42:13.000
TOOK A GUESS
WHERE YOU WERE HEADED.

42:14.959 --> 42:16.500
FIGURING I'D NEED A RIDE?

42:16.500 --> 42:18.834
FIGURED I COULD TALK YOU
OUT OF IT.

42:18.834 --> 42:20.375
NO SUCH LUCK, HUH?

42:20.375 --> 42:22.458
DEB WILL BE DELIGHTED.

42:22.458 --> 42:25.166
AS FAR AS I KNOW,
YOU WENT OUT FOR A WALK.

42:29.917 --> 42:32.333
JESUS, DEX,
DID YOU STEAL SOMETHING?

42:34.166 --> 42:36.250
WELL, MY FINGERPRINTS
WERE ALL OVER IT.

42:36.250 --> 42:38.834
I FIGURED IT WAS PRUDENT
TO GET RID OF THE EVIDENCE.

42:38.834 --> 42:42.166
IT'S JUST A BOX OF ASHES.

42:42.166 --> 42:44.083
JOE WAS CREMATED, THEN.

42:44.083 --> 42:46.709
YEP.

42:46.709 --> 42:48.667
GUESS YOU WEREN'T ABLE
TO FIND OUT

42:48.667 --> 42:50.667
IF HE WAS INJECTED
WITH ANYTHING.

42:50.667 --> 42:52.000
NO.

42:52.000 --> 42:54.500
[ SIGHS ]

42:54.500 --> 42:56.083
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
WITH HIM?

42:56.083 --> 42:57.208
I DON'T KNOW.

43:00.917 --> 43:02.375
HMM, DUMPSTER?

43:04.250 --> 43:06.709
I HAVE A BETTER IDEA.

43:22.750 --> 43:25.208
YOU KNOW...

43:25.208 --> 43:27.125
NO MATTER WHAT HARRY SAID,

43:27.125 --> 43:30.041
NO MATTER WHAT DEB THINKS,

43:30.041 --> 43:32.709
THAT'S YOUR FATHER.

43:32.709 --> 43:34.709
CARDBOARD BOX.

43:34.709 --> 43:37.083
I KNOW YOU DON'T WANT
TO ACKNOWLEDGE IT,

43:37.083 --> 43:39.542
WHICH IS WHY YOU'RE RUNNING
AROUND, BREAKING AND ENTERING,

43:39.542 --> 43:41.750
SEARCHING FOR SOME KILLER.

43:41.750 --> 43:44.625
BUT YOU TOOK THAT

43:44.625 --> 43:47.291
BECAUSE THERE'S
A PART OF YOU

43:47.291 --> 43:50.709
THAT KNOWS THAT THIS...

43:50.709 --> 43:52.291
THAT BOX...

43:52.291 --> 43:55.500
IS YOUR REAL FATHER.

44:13.750 --> 44:15.417
MY FATHER.

44:31.291 --> 44:33.875
SOUNDS STRANGE.

44:33.875 --> 44:35.625
I KNOW.

45:34.000 --> 45:36.000
Rita: OH, HEY.

45:36.000 --> 45:37.709
YOU ALL RIGHT?

45:37.709 --> 45:41.041
[ SIGHS ]
I WAS JUST GETTING SOME AIR.

45:41.041 --> 45:41.834
MMM.

45:45.667 --> 45:49.792
OH, HEY, I FOUND SOMETHING
IN JOE'S CLOSET.

45:49.792 --> 45:53.041
IT'S JUST A BUNCH OF PAPERS.
THEY'RE OVER THERE.

46:07.667 --> 46:10.083
ANY CLUES?

46:19.625 --> 46:21.000
Harry: HEY, BUDDY.

46:21.000 --> 46:23.208
HOW YOU FEELING?

46:23.208 --> 46:24.834
GOOD.

46:24.834 --> 46:27.834
IT KIND OF ITCHES,
BUT THEY HAVE ICE CREAM HERE.

46:27.834 --> 46:29.667
LIFE'S A TRADE-OFF.

46:29.667 --> 46:31.291
WHAT ARE YOU MAKING THERE?

46:31.291 --> 46:33.959
A THANK-YOU CARD.

46:33.959 --> 46:36.625
SEE? THE NURSE BROUGHT ME
THE CRAYONS AND EVERYTHING.

46:36.625 --> 46:38.709
WHO'S IT FOR?

46:38.709 --> 46:41.125
WELL, SHE SAID
I SHOULD THANK

46:41.125 --> 46:43.333
THE MAN
WHO GAVE ME THE BLOOD.

46:43.333 --> 46:48.000
I MEAN, THAT'S NORMAL, RIGHT,
GIVING THANK-YOU CARDS?

46:53.375 --> 46:56.625
YES, IT IS.

46:56.625 --> 46:58.583
IT'S JUST THAT HE'S GONE.

46:58.583 --> 47:00.750
AND WE WON'T BE
SEEING HIM AGAIN.

47:00.750 --> 47:03.417
I'M SORRY.

47:03.417 --> 47:05.709
THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

47:05.709 --> 47:07.417
IT -- IT DOESN'T
REALLY MEAN ANYTHING.

47:16.583 --> 47:19.000
YEAH, IT DOES.

47:19.000 --> 47:21.500
YOU KEEP DRAWING, SON.

47:21.500 --> 47:23.208
I'LL MAKE SURE
IT FINDS HIM.

47:23.208 --> 47:25.834
OKAY.

47:43.458 --> 47:46.834
YOU HAD THE CASE DROPPED?

47:46.834 --> 47:49.041
EXCUSE ME.

47:51.125 --> 47:53.208
I.A. DROPPED DOAKES' CASE.

47:53.208 --> 47:54.625
DO YOU SERIOUSLY THINK

47:54.625 --> 47:55.834
I HAVE ANY SAY
OVER WHAT I.A. DOES?

47:55.834 --> 47:57.542
I PUT EVERYTHING
ON THE LINE.

47:57.542 --> 47:59.041
I TOLD I.A. THE TRUTH,

47:59.041 --> 48:01.291
AND THERE'S A LOT OF EVIDENCE
TO BACK THAT UP.

48:01.291 --> 48:02.834
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

48:02.834 --> 48:04.834
MARIA, I DESERVE TO KNOW.

48:04.834 --> 48:07.250
ALL I KNOW IS THAT I.A.
GOT A CALL

48:07.250 --> 48:08.667
FROM AN AGENCY IN WASHINGTON.

48:08.667 --> 48:10.500
WHAT AGENCY?
I'M GUESSING MILITARY.

48:10.500 --> 48:11.917
THEY SAID THE CASE INVOLVED

48:11.917 --> 48:14.667
SOME SENSITIVE
FOREIGN-RELATIONS ISSUES,

48:14.667 --> 48:16.417
SO THEY WERE GONNA HANDLE IT
FROM THERE.

48:16.417 --> 48:17.750
THEY DISAPPEARED IT.

48:17.750 --> 48:19.792
DOAKES HAD
A HISTORY WITH THEM.

48:19.792 --> 48:21.834
I FIGURED SPECIAL FORCES,
BUT THIS KIND OF REACH --

48:21.834 --> 48:23.500
YOU THINK IT WAS
BLACK OPS, CIA?

48:23.500 --> 48:26.709
MAYBE.

48:26.709 --> 48:28.166
PROBABLY.

48:28.166 --> 48:31.667
AND I RATTED HIM OUT.
JESUS CHRIST.

48:31.667 --> 48:33.375
ANGEL...

48:33.375 --> 48:35.000
YOU DID
WHAT YOU THOUGHT WAS RIGHT.

48:41.583 --> 48:42.917
SQUEAK, SQUEAK.

48:42.917 --> 48:44.875
DO YOU HAVE A PROBLEM?

48:44.875 --> 48:47.625
OFFICER BENSON,

48:47.625 --> 48:49.875
YOU JUST BUMPED
INTO YOUR SUPERIOR.

48:51.166 --> 48:54.875
I BELIEVE YOU OWE
DETECTIVE BATISTA AN APOLOGY!

48:54.875 --> 48:56.083
[ SCOFFS SOFTLY ]

48:57.375 --> 48:59.875
YES, SIR.

48:59.875 --> 49:01.917
[ SIGHS ]
I'M SORRY, SIR.

49:01.917 --> 49:03.709
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

49:40.583 --> 49:41.834
I KNOW I SHOULD BE SORRY

49:41.834 --> 49:44.291
THAT WE MET
UNDER THESE CIRCUMSTANCES,

49:44.291 --> 49:45.834
BUT TRUTHFULLY,

49:45.834 --> 49:47.667
I THINK IT WAS THE BEST WAY
TO GET TO KNOW YOU.

49:50.834 --> 49:53.500
REALTOR SAYS
YOU WON'T GET MUCH FOR IT.

49:53.500 --> 49:54.750
[ SIGHS ]

49:54.750 --> 49:57.875
WELL...MORE THAN
IF I KEPT IT.

49:57.875 --> 50:00.417
ARE WE GOOD?

50:05.417 --> 50:06.959
WE'RE FINE.

50:12.417 --> 50:13.834
ALL RIGHT.

50:13.834 --> 50:16.166
I'LL SEE YOU
BACK AT THE STATION.

50:31.208 --> 50:34.458
CABLE REPAIRMAN.

50:34.458 --> 50:36.959
WAIT! WAIT!

50:36.959 --> 50:38.625
NO, NO, DON'T GO.

50:38.625 --> 50:40.542
WAIT!

50:40.542 --> 50:43.041
PLEASE, I WANT
TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

50:45.000 --> 50:46.750
WAIT!

50:46.750 --> 50:49.500
[ SIGHS ] ALONE AGAIN.

50:49.500 --> 50:52.458
[ SIGHS ] FINALLY.

50:52.458 --> 50:54.583
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

50:54.583 --> 50:57.041
YOU KNOW WHAT?

50:59.333 --> 51:01.709
I'M GLAD YOU WERE HERE.

51:01.709 --> 51:03.083
THOUGHT YOU WOULD BE.

51:06.166 --> 51:09.000
YOO-HOO!

51:09.000 --> 51:12.166
THE CABLE REPAIRMAN --

51:12.166 --> 51:16.208
DID HE SAY ANYTHING
ABOUT MY TV ANTENNA?!

51:18.500 --> 51:19.667
NO!

51:51.000 --> 51:52.709
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

51:55.709 --> 51:57.542
Paul:
RITA, IT'S ME.

52:00.750 --> 52:02.250
THEY'RE ASLEEP.

52:02.250 --> 52:04.709
YEAH, WELL, I SHOULD HAVE
BEEN HERE, OKAY?

52:04.709 --> 52:06.083
IT'S LATE AND YOU'RE DRUNK

52:06.083 --> 52:08.208
AND YOU CAN'T KEEP
COMING BY HERE UNANNOUNCED.

52:08.208 --> 52:11.542
YOU DON'T CALL
THE SHOTS, OKAY?

52:11.542 --> 52:13.000
LOOK, PAUL,
I WANT YOU TO LEAVE.

52:13.000 --> 52:14.917
I DON'T GIVE
A FUCK WHAT YOU WANT.

52:14.917 --> 52:16.792
I WANT MY FUCKING KIDS!

52:16.792 --> 52:19.083
YOU'RE GONNA SCARE THEM.
THEY DON'T WANT TO SEE ME?

52:19.083 --> 52:21.208
THOSE KIDS
ARE GONNA REMEMBER

52:21.208 --> 52:22.792
WHO THE HEAD
OF THIS FUCKING FAMILY IS.

52:22.792 --> 52:23.875
HEY!

52:23.875 --> 52:27.125
YOU'RE RIGHT.

52:27.125 --> 52:28.875
I'VE BEEN AWFUL.

52:28.875 --> 52:31.917
I-I JUST DIDN'T REALIZE
I WAS HURTING YOU SO MUCH.

52:31.917 --> 52:34.458
BUT I CAN MAKE IT UP TO YOU.

52:34.458 --> 52:36.250
LET ME TRY.

52:50.959 --> 52:54.333
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

52:54.333 --> 52:56.500
WANT TO PLAY ROUGH?
HUH? IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?

52:56.500 --> 52:57.917
NO! NO!

52:57.917 --> 52:59.792
FUCK YOU, WHORE.

52:59.792 --> 53:02.667
COME ON.

53:02.667 --> 53:03.417
COME ON!

53:03.417 --> 53:04.667
UGH!

53:04.667 --> 53:06.625
[ GROANING ]

53:12.917 --> 53:16.875
WAKE UP. WAKE UP.
COME ON.

53:16.875 --> 53:18.458
OHH.

53:35.083 --> 53:40.125
♪ GOES THROUGH THE CIRCLE
FAST AND SLOW ♪

53:40.125 --> 53:42.792
♪ I KNOW ♪

53:42.792 --> 53:45.875
♪ IT CAN'T STOP, I WONDER ♪

53:49.792 --> 53:53.291
♪ I WANT TO KNOW ♪

53:53.291 --> 53:56.333
I HAD A FATHER...

53:56.333 --> 54:00.834
SOMEONE OTHER THAN HARRY
WHO CALLED ME SON.

54:00.834 --> 54:03.417
THE THOUGHT
NEVER EVEN OCCURRED TO ME.

54:03.417 --> 54:06.583
HARRY WAS ALL I NEEDED.

54:06.583 --> 54:10.250
IT WAS HARRY
WHO ALWAYS HAD THE ANSWERS.

54:10.250 --> 54:14.709
HE KNEW WHO WAS
GOOD, BAD, SAFE...

54:14.709 --> 54:16.834
AND DANGEROUS.

54:16.834 --> 54:19.583
I BUILT MY LIFE
ON HARRY'S CODE.

54:19.583 --> 54:22.000
I LIVED BY IT.

54:22.000 --> 54:24.000
BUT HARRY LIED.

54:24.000 --> 54:26.333
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

54:26.333 --> 54:28.917
WHAT ELSE DON'T I KNOW?

54:28.917 --> 54:32.959
MY CONCRETE FOUNDATION
IS TURNING TO SHIFTING SAND.

54:32.959 --> 54:34.667
MAYBE RUDY WAS RIGHT --

54:34.667 --> 54:37.208
